JOHANNESBURG - Traffic came to a standstill on the N1 highway near the Maraisburg and Gordon off-ramps in Roodepoort on Tuesday afternoon after a train caught fire on the bridge above the highway. Authorities were at the scene and no injuries were reported It is not known what caused the train to catch fire. Police are investigating the incident. The public took to social media to warn motorists to be vigilant around Maraisburg. eNCA